Package: dScoreTest
Title: Debiased Score Tests for Nonparametric Goodness of Fit
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Richard Guo [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2081-7398>), 
    Aditya Dhawan [aut]
Maintainer: Richard Guo <ricguo@umich.edu>
Authors@R: c(person("Richard", "Guo", , "ricguo@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2081-7398")), 
      person("Aditya", "Dhawan", email = "abc@abc.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Implements debiased score tests for nonparametric goodness-of-fit
    testing. Provides tests for generalised additive models (GAMs), quantile
    GAMs, and heterogeneous treatment effects in partially linear models.
    The framework uses sample splitting and non-parametric hunting via
    generalised random forests to find directions of model misspecification,
    then forms a debiased test statistic with correct asymptotic size.
